lead_paragraph: Alex Rodriguez homered for the first time since coming off the disabled list, Masahiro Tanaka pitched seven shutout innings and the New York Yankees beat the Tampa Bay Rays 4-1 on Friday night.

headline.print_headline: A-Rod, Tanaka Lead Yankees Past Rays 4-1
